data.name: textBox_info.Text
data.value:
A simple assistant to help you stay online in some games when you need to take small breaks. Please use responsibly and do not take extended breaks while using this application.
Despite using a simple method of pressing both mouse buttons almost simultaneously, there is no guarantee that this application is safe under the terms of service of any game. Use it at your own risk.
If this has been useful to you, please consider supporting my work by clicking on the button below. Thank you!

data.name: textBox_warning.Text
data.value: - You MUST keep the cursor on top of the game for this to work. I also suggest capping the framerate to save energy. - To keep this application as non-intrusive as possible, there are no checks to confirm if you have the game focused or not. - Upon pressing Start, there will be a 5 second wait before the first press. Take this time to place your cursor correctly. - Failure to follow the steps above might: 1) Cause the application to do nothing; 2) Cause undesirable and unpredictable interactions with other applications due to simulating mouse clicks.
